  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><br>Lavrynthos is <strong>an independently created VR short, a funny and philosophic story</strong> that places you at the heart of the labyrinth of Crete to tell you the story of the unlikely relationship between the Minotaur and his next meal: a girl named Cora. <br><br>In this experience, you'll get lost in a huge maze. You'll obviously want to find your way out, don't you ?  Well, actually... maybe you won't. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dive into a contemporary Greek tragedy</strong> paying homage to modern dramatic theory while challenging it at the same time. Lavrynthos is a humorous take on a 3000 years old myth. Navigate an infinite non-euclidean maze that shifts space and time. What will you find?  Lavrynthos will distort your sense of direction, space and balance and you might even <strong> find yourself lost inside your own bedroom</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Created with support of the Venice Biennale College, Lavrythos premiered at Venice Film Festival and in 2022 won the Stereopsia Crystal Owl <strong>Award for Best Creative Experience</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/0c810993b4fc95cd4614ffb1d9a13416.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><br>Lavrynthos is <strong>an independently created VR short, a funny and philosophic story</strong> that places you at the heart of the labyrinth of Crete to tell you the story of the unlikely relationship between the Minotaur and his next meal: a girl named Cora. <br><br>In this experience, you'll get lost in a huge maze. You'll obviously want to find your way out, don't you ?  Well, actually... maybe you won't. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/a10c0333bd4383369985c56629d67dbf.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dive into a contemporary Greek tragedy</strong> paying homage to modern dramatic theory while challenging it at the same time. Lavrynthos is a humorous take on a 3000 years old myth. Navigate an infinite non-euclidean maze that shifts space and time. What will you find?  Lavrynthos will distort your sense of direction, space and balance and you might even <strong> find yourself lost inside your own bedroom</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/807c5f325f956d5b6b688bd4c728273b.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Created with support of the Venice Biennale College, Lavrythos premiered at Venice Film Festival and in 2022 won the Stereopsia Crystal Owl <strong>Award for Best Creative Experience</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.poster.avif?t=1686039247\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.webm?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025810/extras/add64eeb7d5f0595ca948c4041fac4ad.mp4?t=1686039247\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
